\@writefile{lot}{\contentsline {table}{\numberline {13}{\ignorespaces Harness ablation. Three harnesses tested on 30 synthetic tasks $\times $ 3 repetitions. H1 = minimal ReAct (baseline); H2 = single-shot (one LLM call, complete code); H3 = few-shot ReAct (ReAct + 1 worked example). Silent failures persist across all three harnesses for GPT-4o, confirming they are not an artifact of the minimal ReAct design. DeepSeek-V3 cells are partial due to long API latencies.\relax }}{11}{table.caption.20}\protected@file@percent }
